4.31	Ralph_McGehee	Ralph McGehee	A downside of this book for many was McGehee's personal knowledge of the extent to which the famed physician, Thomas Anthony Dooley III, was involved in CIA warfare across Indochina. This included awareness that the atrocities alleged in the best seller, "Deliver Us From Evil", 1956, were fabricated for the beginning of a psywar campaign (later revealed by the Church Committee in 1975).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d7/Mcgeheenotredame.jpg/220px-Mcgeheenotredame.jpg
